Through our lives, jobs, families circles and friendships God has uniquely placed in our lives, we are to commit our lives to demonstrating God's immeasurable love as best as we can. When Jesus preached to the crowds in the Book of Luke, he was quick to say that we are called to love those who are hard to love - not just the ones that love you in return. August Church exists to do just that - express God's unending love and mercy to those that need it the most. Jesus said it best in Luke 6:35-38:
